<title>USA: Park buys Ohio foundry from Manoir Industries.</title>
<headline>Park buys Ohio foundry from Manoir Industries.</headline>
<dateline>CLEVELAND 1997-07-09</dateline>
<text>
<p>Park Corp said Wednesday it bought foundry Manoir Electroalloys Corp from Manoir Industries of France for an undisclosed price.</p>
<p>Park Corp said it would operate the company, which is located in Elyria, Ohio, under the name Electroalloys Corp.</p>
<p>A spokesman was not immediately available for comment.</p>
